# Streaming Text Animation

AI chat responses must always print in smoothly and elegantly — word by word with a soft fade and blur transition. Never render streaming text as rigid chunky blocks.

## Implementation

- Use the `StreamingWords` component for all streaming assistant messages
- Each word fades in individually with a staggered delay (30ms per word, max 8 words stagger)
- Animation: opacity 0→1 + blur 2px→0px over 0.4s ease-out
- CSS class: `.streaming-word` in `globals.css`
- Once streaming completes, render the final formatted text without animation spans
